strings:
<voice_0x010015FB><se_low>Juggerwroth: Gwaaaaaargh! No... NO!
How could mere humans get the better of
the great Juggerwroth!?

<voice_0x010015FC><se_low>Juggerwroth: Haha! You really thought you had?
Idiots! I-DI-OTS!

<voice_0x010015FD><se_low>Yangus: Wot's goin' on?
Everyfin' feels 'eavy all of a sudden!
<voice_0x010015FE><se_high>Jessica: What...what's he done to us?
<voice_0x010015FF><se_def>Angelo: Ah. Now that...is cheating.

<voice_0x01001600><se_high>Red: Ohh...'ow'd I let meself get dragged into
this mess...?
<voice_0x01001601><se_low>Morrie: Aaaaaayiii!
<voice_0x01001602><se_low>Juggerwroth: Ha HA! IDIOTS! That is what you get for letting your guard down!

<voice_0x01001603><se_low>Juggerwroth: Still...my strength is not what it was.
Then again, it is difficult to flex your muscles when you have been turned to STONE.
<voice_0x01001604><se_low>Juggerwroth: Speaking of weakness, how does it feel to be crushed by your own weight?

<voice_0x01001605><se_low>Juggerwroth: Oh, but do not fret. I am no monster.
It shall be my pleasure to end your suffering...
IN ONE FELL SWOOP!

<voice_0x01001606><se_low>Juggerwroth: What!?
My, my spell is BROKEN!

<voice_0x01001607><se_def>Marcello: Dear me, what a disappointment.
You so nearly had it in the bag.
<voice_0x01001608><se_def>Angelo: Marcello! What are you doing here?

<voice_0x01001609><se_low>Yangus: Whoa, yer Angelo's bruv, intcha?
Wot you doin' 'ere?
<voice_0x0100160A><se_high>Jessica: Marcello! What are you doing here?
<voice_0x0100160B><se_low>Juggerwroth: MORE humans? Gargh! You creatures get everywhere! Just how big IS your little party?

<voice_0x0100160C><se_def>Marcello: Oh, we're not together.
Most certainly not.
<voice_0x0100160D><se_low>Juggerwroth: No matter. You will DIE together.
<voice_0x0100160E><se_low>Juggerwroth: Prepare to SUFFER, you meddling little worm!
<voice_0x0100160F><se_low>Juggerwroth: ...Unlike the rest, I mean to kill you SLOWLY.

<voice_0x01001610><se_def>Marcello: Hmph, I'm hearing a lot of talk,
but not seeing much action.

<voice_0x01001611><se_def>Marcello: How about we dispense with the chatter and you let me do what I came here to do?
By which I mean ‘destroy you’.

<voice_0x01001612><se_low>Juggerwroth: You dare to make light of ME!? GRRRAAAH!
I shall grind your bones into DUST!

<voice_0x01001613><se_def>Marcello: It seems he's finally ready to fight.
Try not to get under my feet, will you?
